        "details": {
            "description": "<p>Blood flows from the fanged skull rune as if it were an open wound.</p>",
            "disable": "<p><span data-pf2-check=\"religion\" data-pf2-traits=\"complex,haunt\" data-pf2-label=\"Exorcise Spirit DC\" data-pf2-dc=\"20\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\">Religion</span> (trained) to exorcise the spirit, <span data-pf2-check=\"religion\" data-pf2-traits=\"complex,haunt\" data-pf2-label=\"Sever Spiritual Connection DC\" data-pf2-dc=\"21\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\">Religion</span> or <span data-pf2-check=\"occultism\" data-pf2-traits=\"complex,haunt\" data-pf2-label=\"Sever Spiritual Connection DC\" data-pf2-dc=\"21\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\">Occultism</span> (trained) to sever the connection between <em>Hunger's Call</em> and the temple, or <span data-pf2-check=\"crafting\" data-pf2-traits=\"complex,haunt\" data-pf2-label=\"Break up the Mural\" data-pf2-dc=\"21\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\">Crafting</span> (trained) to break up the pattern of the mural; three total successes are required to disable the haunt.</p>",
            "isComplex": true,
            "level": {
                "value": 3
            },
            "reset": "<p>The mosaic ceases its routine 2 rounds after all living creatures are out of sight of the stairs. After 6 hours the haunt is ready to trigger again.</p>",
            "routine": "<p><span class=\"pf2-icon\">3</span> The bloody mosaic blasts shards of colored glass at anyone within 10 feet of the eastern wall, and they each take [[/r 1d10 #slashing]]{1d10 slashing damage} plus [[/r 1 #persistent bleed]] @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Persistent Damage]{Persistent Bleed Damage} (<span data-pf2-check=\"reflex\" data-pf2-traits=\"complex,haunt,slashing,damaging-effect\" data-pf2-label=\"Avoid the Glass Shards DC\" data-pf2-dc=\"20\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\">basic Reflex</span> save; critical success negates the bleed damage).</p>"
        },
